com.adobe.cq.social.filelibrary.client.api

Interface Asset<T extends CommentCollectionConfiguration>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comment<T>, SocialCollectionComponent, SocialComponent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Document
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAsset

    public interface Asset<T extends CommentCollectionConfiguration>
extends Comment<T>
    An Asset represents a document or a folder in a FileLibrary. A folder can only contain sub-folders or documents. A document is represented as an attachment of a comment. An asset is represented as a comment, or a reply of a comment, depending on the level of the asset relative to its parents.
